comments: Ingram (NOP) does not place his hand underneath the ball during his dribble.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) steps into Murphy II's (NOP) body and initiates contact that affects his SQBR as he secures the loose ball.
Jones (NOP) and Bane (MEM) mutually engage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) turns to roll and marginal contact occurs with McCollum (NOP) as he navigates under the pick.
Nance Jr. (NOP) establishes a legal position in Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path and he absorbs the marginal body contact when they come together at the end of the drive.
Bane (MEM) moves into Ingram's (NOP) path and initiates body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Nance Jr. (NOP) steps slightly forward and marginal body contact occurs with Jackson Jr. (MEM) during his shot attempt near the rim.
Ingram (NOP) moves his pivot foot heel-to-toe to create distance.
Brooks (MEM) jumps forward as he contests and initiates body contact with Ingram (NOP) that affects the jump shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) is moving alongside Ingram's (NOP) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Jones (MEM) commits a take foul on Murphy II (NOP).
Jones (NOP) makes contact with Brooks' (MEM) arm after the release that affects his follow-through on the jump shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) wipes away Jones' (MEM) arm and the contact affects his ability to defend the inbound pass.
Richardson (NOP) commits a take foul on Bane (MEM).
Nance Jr. (NOP) reaches in and initiates illegal arm contact with Jackson Jr. (MEM) that affects his SQBR after securing the rebound.
